description.plain:
Näääk (Matar Henrikki Samba), born March 29, 1983 in Stockholm, is a Swedish rapper. He has a Finnish mother and a Gambian father. He lived in the early years of his life in Rinkeby, Stockholm, but moved as a teenager to Gullmarsplan

On October 21, 2009 his debut album was released “Näääk vem?” (Näääk who?). He played at the Siesta Music festival in 2010 and at Bråvalla festival in 2013.

At Kingsizegalan 2013, he won the Best Solo Artist Award and Best Album Award “Mannen utan mask” (The man Without Mask).
